    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition overall and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected without any hesitation. While the car shows some minor signs of regular use, such as a few small stone chips on the front bumper and light wear on the interior upholstery, it remains mechanically sound and visually appealing. All major systems, including the climate control and infotainment, are fully functional. This car offers a reliable driving experience and has plenty of life left for its next owner.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly way to get on the road? This car is a solid, functional choice that still has plenty of life left! While it proudly shows some cosmetic wear and minor character from its time on the road, it\u2019s a dependable driver that gets the job done. It's a fantastic opportunity for someone who values utility and reliability at a great price point!",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior paint still holds a deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scratch on the rear passenger door. The interior is clean and well-preserved, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and all power features working as they should. Mechanically, the car performs reliably; it has a documented service history, a smooth-shifting transmission, and the engine runs quietly. This is a solid, dependable car that shows pride of ownership without being a garage queen.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, representing a premier choice for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, this automobile has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for roadworthiness and longevity. Offering a sophisticated balance of performance and value, it stands as a testament to diligent ownership and remains in commendable condition. Experience the assurance of a vehicle prepared for the road ahead by a dealership committed to professional excellence.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in wonderful shape, runs smoothly, and has been well-loved and taken care of over the years. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is totally ready for its next adventure with you! I'm looking for a quick sale, so come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 B32 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The high-revving valvetrain is synchronized by a double-VANOS system, ensuring optimal torque across the rev range. Power is delivered via a precise six-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut with a reinforced subframe and refreshed bushings, while the suspension geometry provides exceptional turn-in and lateral grip. Meticulously maintained with a focus on mechanical integrity and drivetrain longevity, this example represents a balanced, driver-focused machine ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a stellar example of a well-cared-for daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor, superficial road wear expected from a vehicle that has been driven with pride. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and inviting; the upholstery is free of tears or significant stains, the dashboard is crack-free, and all electronic features\u2014including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having benefited from a consistent schedule of synthetic oil changes and preventative maintenance. The engine runs smoothly without any hesitation, the transmission shifts are crisp and seamless, and the suspension provides a comfortable, quiet ride. With a set of high-tread tires and recently serviced brakes, this car is turn-key and ready for its next adventure. It offers a premium driving experience without the brand-new price tag.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
