      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, demonstrating a consistent history of care and mechanical integrity. Its presentation remains impressive, reflecting a standard of ownership that ensures both immediate reliability and long-term value. This offering represents a sophisticated choice for the discerning driver seeking a premier balance of performance and proven durability.",
      "price": 34900.0,
